    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone seeking a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are solid and have been regularly maintained, the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and minor paint fading. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few stains, but all essential features like the AC and radio remain fully operational. It is a reliable runner that is priced to reflect its cosmetic imperfections and current mileage.",
