    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
