    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s dream, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The powertrain utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically sound with documented rod bearing service and a robust subframe, this unit features the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system for precision handling. The variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution during spirited cornering. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical components are dialed in for high-performance use.",
